			"width": 335.15625,
			"height": 260,
			"text": "---\nname: excalidraw-diagram\ndescription: Create Excalidraw diagram JSON\n  files that make visual arguments. Use when\n  the user wants to visualize workflows,\n  architectures, or concepts.\n---\n\n# Instructions\n\nGenerate .excalidraw JSON files that ARGUE,\nnot just display information.\n\n## References\n- color-palette.md\n- element-templates.md",
			"originalText": "---\nname: excalidraw-diagram\ndescription: Create Excalidraw diagram JSON\n  files that make visual arguments. Use when\n  the user wants to visualize workflows,\n  architectures, or concepts.\n---\n\n# Instructions\n\nGenerate .excalidraw JSON files that ARGUE,\nnot just display information.\n\n## References\n- color-palette.md\n- element-templates.md",
